 src/gcc/config/loongarch/constraints.md         |  4 ----
 src/gcc/config/loongarch/loongarch.md           | 17 -----------------
 src/gcc/config/loongarch/predicates.md          |  9 ++-------
 .../testsuite/gcc.target/loongarch/bstrins-4.c  |  9 +++++++++
 4 files changed, 11 insertions(+), 28 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 src/gcc/testsuite/gcc.target/loongarch/bstrins-4.c

